  "detailed_description": "<h1>SEE OUR OTHER GAMES</h1><p><br><br></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/1ebb3cc7b27371f46d79edf8acce714d.poster.avif?t=1651966567\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/1ebb3cc7b27371f46d79edf8acce714d.webm?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/1ebb3cc7b27371f46d79edf8acce714d.mp4?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>In <strong>INVERT </strong>the player will be challenged to solve several logic challenges. You must move in a limited way and make all bases turn white or all bases turn black. When jumping over a base, the same color changes and you'll use this to your advantage.<br>Get ready for a challenging experience and challenge yourself while listening to a calm and relaxing soundtrack.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/b78f64736d56ae857e67a823fba5ad34.poster.avif?t=1651966567\" width=616 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/b78f64736d56ae857e67a823fba5ad34.webm?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1774700/extras/b78f64736d56ae857e67a823fba5ad34.mp4?t=1651966567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Characteristics:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Use the mechanic of changing the base color to make all bases the same.<br></li><li>You have a limited amount of moves, adding a little more challenge to gameplay.<br></li><li>45 Stages with difficulty levels from easy to hard stages.<br></li><li>Calm and relaxing soundtrack.<br></li><li></li></ul>",
